      <p class="body-font">
        Bicycle rights Portland master cleanse, direct trade fixie hella banh mi irony gluten-free trust fund ugh. Vinyl selvage selfies, church-key Cosby sweater letterpress semiotics chambray hella. Roof party Tonx McSweeney's tote bag vinyl. Pork belly fap ethnic cred Tumblr locavore. Schlitz keffiyeh Cosby sweater butcher, Blue Bottle leggings Marfa High Life Williamsburg before they sold out tofu chambray. Cornhole tattooed meggings Cosby sweater iPhone, single-origin coffee bitters 8-bit forage. Neutra PBR&B messenger bag, pork belly deep v narwhal next level.

        Lomo leggings selfies, banh mi four loko before they sold out pug readymade PBR&B raw denim dreamcatcher. Cardigan you probably haven't heard of them iPhone, Truffaut slow-carb Marfa forage viral organic photo booth lomo art party chia. Butcher post-ironic salvia, locavore banjo raw denim pour-over Godard gentrify DIY Tonx. Fanny pack actually Williamsburg, you probably haven't heard of them literally ugh stumptown Wes Anderson messenger bag. Four loko lo-fi McSweeney's, scenester tote bag fashion axe selfies squid sriracha seitan gentrify. Biodiesel tattooed retro, gentrify ennui High Life XOXO VHS direct trade Austin church-key. Hella small batch messenger bag, Austin fixie PBR&B post-ironic Tumblr chia Odd Future occupy jean shorts locavore wolf mumblecore.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div>
    <div class="profile-content">
      <h2 class="header-font">My Trips!</h2>
      <table>
        <thead class="header-font">
          <td>Date</td>
          <td>Time</td>
          <td>Location</td>
          <td>Destination</td>
          <td>Spaces</td>
        </thead>
        <% current_user.trips.each do |trip| %>
        <tbody class="body-font">
          <tr>
            <td><%= trip.date %></td>
            <td><%= trip.time %></td>
            <td><%= trip.location %></td>
            <td><%= trip.destination %></td>
            <td><%= trip.spaces %></td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
        <% end %>
      </table>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div id="trip-form" class="side-bar">
  <div class="form-container">
      <h2>Creating a new trip!</h2>
      <% trip = Trip.new %>
    <%= form_for trip do |f| %>
      <!-- Select a date: <input type="text" id="datepicker" /><br /> -->
      Pick a date: <%= f.date_field :date %><br />
      Select a time: <%= f.select :time, ["7:00am", "7:15am", "7:30am", "7:45am", "8:00am"] %><br />
      Select a location: <%= f.text_field :location %><br />
      Select a destination: <%= f.text_field :destination %><br />
      How many spaces are available: <%= f.text_field :spaces %><br />
      <%= f.submit %>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>
